{"id":132463,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/01/时代图集-突尼斯示威者推翻独裁政府/","date":"2011-01-16T07:00:08Z","modified":"2011-01-16T07:00:08Z","title":"时代图集: 突尼斯示威者推翻独裁政府","content":"<p>核心提示：突尼斯总统扎因·阿比丁·本·阿里(Zine al-Abidine Ben Ali下)</p>\n<p>在面临诉求就业保障和民主的示威运动此起彼伏的局面时选择了出逃。</p>\n<div><a href=\"http://www.time.com/time/photogallery/0,29307,2042614_2226828,00.html\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://img.timeinc.net/time/photoessays/2011/tunisia_riots/tunisia_riots_01.jpg\" alt=\"Protesters in Tunisia Bring Down the Government\" width=\"611\" height=\"404\" /></a></div>\n<div>街头</div>\n<div>2011年1月14日，星期五，突尼斯市，一名示威者在同警察的冲突期间向警察局投掷石块。突尼斯总统本·阿里在宣布该国进入全国紧急状态之后，旋即逃离出国。.</div>\n<div><img src=\"http://img.timeinc.net/time/photoessays/2011/tunisia_riots/tunisia_riots_02.jpg\" alt=\"Protesters in Tunisia Bring Down the Government\" /></div>\n<div>燃烧</div>\n<div>在突尼斯市的示威者和警察的对峙期间，一<em>缕浓烟升起。在出逃之前，</em>本·阿里为平息局势而解散了政府。他要求在六个月之后提前举行议会选举。</div>\n<div><img src=\"http://img.timeinc.net/time/photoessays/2011/tunisia_riots/tunisia_riots_03.jpg\" alt=\"Protesters in Tunisia Bring Down the Government\" /></div>\n<div>万众齐心</div>\n<div>示威者高呼反对突尼斯总统的口号。总理穆罕默德·加努希(<em>Mohamed Ghannouchi</em>)在国家电视台上向全国发表讲话，并宣布他已经接管本·阿里成为过渡总统。</div>\n<div><img src=\"http://img.timeinc.net/time/photoessays/2011/tunisia_riots/tunisia_riots_04.jpg\" alt=\"Protesters in Tunisia Bring Down the Government\" /></div>\n<div>言词争辩</div>\n<div>加入到示威队伍的律师们在内政部门前高呼口号。因为抗议就业和生活压力的加剧而引发的示威浪潮最终转变为对本·阿里铁腕政权的直接挑战。</div>\n<div><img src=\"http://img.timeinc.net/time/photoessays/2011/tunisia_riots/tunisia_riots_05.jpg\" alt=\"Protesters in Tunisia Bring Down the Government\" /></div>\n<div>齐心协力<br />\n示威者手举写有“本·阿里，滚蛋”的标语牌。</div>\n<div><img src=\"http://img.timeinc.net/time/photoessays/2011/tunisia_riots/tunisia_riots_06.jpg\" alt=\"Protesters in Tunisia Bring Down the Government\" /></div>\n<div>失控</div>\n<div>1月14日，星期五，在突尼斯市中心大道上的示威者同警察对峙期间，一名突尼斯士兵在试图去让群情激愤的示威者平静下来时发出尖叫声。</div>\n<div><img src=\"http://img.timeinc.net/time/photoessays/2011/tunisia_riots/tunisia_riots_07.jpg\" alt=\"Protesters in Tunisia Bring Down the Government\" /></div>\n<div>急转弯</div>\n<div>冲突期间，暴民在踢打一名警察。</div>\n<div><img src=\"http://img.timeinc.net/time/photoessays/2011/tunisia_riots/tunisia_riots_08.jpg\" alt=\"Protesters in Tunisia Bring Down the Government\" /></div>\n<div>鄙视当局<br />\n一名示威者点燃了一顶警察帽。</div>\n<div><img src=\"http://img.timeinc.net/time/photoessays/2011/tunisia_riots/tunisia_riots_09.jpg\" alt=\"Protesters in Tunisia Bring Down the Government\" /></div>\n<div>昏厥</div>\n<div>在一次催泪瓦斯袭击之后，一名突尼斯士兵查看一位失去知觉的暴民。</div>\n<div><img src=\"http://img.timeinc.net/time/photoessays/2011/tunisia_riots/tunisia_riots_10.jpg\" alt=\"Protesters in Tunisia Bring Down the Government\" /></div>\n<div>烟尘滚滚</div>\n<div>冲突期间，一名示威者避开催泪瓦斯的袭击。</div>\n","author":296,"categories":[20534],"tags":[9265,9553,15021,15284]}